Name: id
Create table query: CREATE TABLE "listinginfo" (	"id"	TEXT NOT NULL,	"school"	TEXT,	"name"	TEXT,	"address"	TEXT,	"city"	TEXT,	"province"	TEXT,	"postal_code"	TEXT,	"type_accom"	TEXT,	"price"	INTEGER,	"start_date"	INTEGER,	"lease_type"	INTEGER,	"url"	TEXT,	"ac"	NUMERIC,	"furnished"	NUMERIC,	"laundry"	NUMERIC,	"parking"	NUMERIC,	"longitude"	NUMERIC,	"latitude"	NUMERIC,	"image_url"	NUMERIC,	"distance"	NUMERIC,	"uploaddate"	NUMERIC,	PRIMARY KEY("id"));

Name: type_accom
Note: type of accomodation: House, Apartment, Other

Name: start_date
Note: 0 means "Available now!", others in the format:"1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC"

Name: distance
Note: The distance to school (based on school code), add dictionary to store school address
